  <summary>&lt;strong&gt;Welcome to Integrating Technology in the Adult Education Classroom!&lt;/strong&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Purpose:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span data-scheme-color="@000000,1," data-usefontface="true" data-contrast="none" xml:lang="EN-US" lang="EN-US"&gt;This self-paced course is designed for&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-scheme-color="@000000,1," data-usefontface="true" data-contrast="none" xml:lang="EN-US" lang="EN-US"&gt;adult education&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-scheme-color="@000000,1," data-usefontface="true" data-contrast="none" xml:lang="EN-US" lang="EN-US"&gt;instructors, trainers, and coordinators, particularly those in adult basic education (ABE),&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-scheme-color="@000000,1," data-usefontface="true" data-contrast="none" xml:lang="EN-US" lang="EN-US"&gt;adult special education (ASE), English language acquisition (ELA), and STEM career technical&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-scheme-color="@000000,1," data-usefontface="true" data-contrast="none" xml:lang="EN-US" lang="EN-US"&gt;education.&amp;nbsp;&lt;span data-scheme-color="@000000,1," data-usefontface="true" data-contrast="none" xml:lang="EN-US" lang="EN-US"&gt;It is made up of three units that examine the&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-scheme-color="@000000,1," data-usefontface="true" data-contrast="none" xml:lang="EN-US" lang="EN-US"&gt;following&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-scheme-color="@000000,1," data-usefontface="true" data-contrast="none" xml:lang="EN-US" lang="EN-US"&gt;&lt;em&gt;why&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-scheme-color="@000000,1," data-usefontface="true" data-contrast="none" xml:lang="EN-US" lang="EN-US"&gt;,&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-scheme-color="@000000,1," data-usefontface="true" data-contrast="none" xml:lang="EN-US" lang="EN-US"&gt;&lt;em&gt;how&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-scheme-color="@000000,1," data-usefontface="true" data-contrast="none" xml:lang="EN-US" lang="EN-US"&gt;,&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-scheme-color="@000000,1," data-usefontface="true" data-contrast="none" xml:lang="EN-US" lang="EN-US"&gt;and&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-scheme-color="@000000,1," data-usefontface="true" data-contrast="none" xml:lang="EN-US" lang="EN-US"&gt;&lt;em&gt;what&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-scheme-color="@000000,1," data-usefontface="true" data-contrast="none" xml:lang="EN-US" lang="EN-US"&gt;&amp;nbsp;questions&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-scheme-color="@000000,1," data-usefontface="true" data-contrast="none" xml:lang="EN-US" lang="EN-US"&gt;about&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-scheme-color="@000000,1," data-usefontface="true" data-contrast="none" xml:lang="EN-US" lang="EN-US"&gt;integrating technology&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-scheme-color="@000000,1," data-usefontface="true" data-contrast="none" xml:lang="EN-US" lang="EN-US"&gt;into&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-scheme-color="@000000,1," data-usefontface="true" data-contrast="none" xml:lang="EN-US" lang="EN-US"&gt;the adult&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-scheme-color="@000000,1," data-usefontface="true" data-contrast="none" xml:lang="EN-US" lang="EN-US"&gt;education classroom:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-scheme-color="@000000,1," data-usefontface="true" data-contrast="none" xml:lang="EN-US" lang="EN-US"&gt;&lt;span data-scheme-color="@000000,1," data-usefontface="true" data-contrast="none" xml:lang="EN-US" lang="EN-US"&gt;&lt;img src="@@PLUGINFILE@@/why-what-how.png?time=1697460478311" alt="Circle that contains the words what, where, and why" width="200" height="205" class="atto_image_button_left"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class="editor-indent" style="margin-left: 30px;"&gt;&lt;span data-usefontface="true" data-contrast="none" xml:lang="EN-US" lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 1.2rem;"&gt;&lt;em&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;\( \bullet \)&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;Why&lt;/em&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-usefontface="true" data-contrast="none" xml:lang="EN-US" lang="EN-US"&gt;is technology important for instruction and learning?&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;​&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-scheme-color="@000000,1," data-usefontface="true" data-contrast="none" xml:lang="EN-US" lang="EN-US"&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class="editor-indent" style="margin-left: 30px;"&gt;&lt;span data-scheme-color="@000000,1," data-usefontface="true" data-contrast="none" xml:lang="EN-US" lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 1.2rem;"&gt;&lt;em&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-scheme-color="@000000,1," data-usefontface="true" data-contrast="none" xml:lang="EN-US" lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 1.2rem;"&gt;&lt;em&gt;\( \bullet \)&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;How&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-scheme-color="@000000,1," data-usefontface="true" data-contrast="none" xml:lang="EN-US" lang="EN-US"&gt;&amp;nbsp;do you approach integrating technology?&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;​&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class="editor-indent" style="margin-left: 30px;"&gt;&lt;span data-usefontface="true" data-contrast="none" xml:lang="EN-US" lang="EN-US"&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class="editor-indent" style="margin-left: 30px;"&gt;&lt;span data-usefontface="true" data-contrast="none" xml:lang="EN-US" lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 1.2rem;"&gt;&lt;em&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;\( \bullet \)&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;What&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-usefontface="true" data-contrast="none" xml:lang="EN-US" lang="EN-US"&gt;&amp;nbsp;tools can you use to integrate technology?&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;For the culminating activity, you will complete a Technology&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-scheme-color="@000000,1," data-usefontface="true" data-contrast="none" xml:lang="EN-US" lang="EN-US"&gt;Integration Action Plan for a unit or lesson.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Commitment:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;This course will take approximately 5 hours to complete. You must complete all units and assessments to earn a certificate.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Objectives:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;After completing this course, you will be able to do the following:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
    &lt;li&gt;&lt;span data-usefontface="false" data-contrast="none" xml:lang="EN-US" lang="EN-US"&gt;understand the benefits of using technology tools for instructional&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-usefontface="false" data-contrast="none" xml:lang="EN-US" lang="EN-US"&gt;purposes;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;​&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
    &lt;li&gt;&lt;span data-usefontface="false" data-contrast="none" xml:lang="EN-US" lang="EN-US"&gt;develop your own Technology Integration Action Plan; and&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
    &lt;li&gt;&lt;span&gt;locate new technology tools as they are required.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;This course is composed of the following:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
